# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:23
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "En savoir plus"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:24
msgid ""
"We are working hard to expand this user guide and to improve OpenShot Video "
"Editor, but if you are stuck and don't know where to turn, OpenShot has "
"several sources for additional information."
msgstr ""
"Nous travaillons dur pour enrichir ce guide utilisateur et améliorer "
"OpenShot Video Editor, mais si vous êtes bloqué et ne savez pas vers qui "
"vous tourner, OpenShot propose plusieurs sources d'informations "
"supplémentaires."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:27
msgid ""
"OpenShot has several `YouTube Tutorials <https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ available to help you learn more."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot propose plusieurs `tutoriels YouTube <https://www.youtube.com/"
"playlist?list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ pour vous aider à en "
"apprendre davantage."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:28
msgid ""
"OpenShot has a `Reddit User Community <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"dedicated to users helping users, answering questions, and discussing video "
"editing and OpenShot topics."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot dispose d'une `communauté d'utilisateurs Reddit <https://openshot."
"org/forum>`_ dédiée à l'entraide entre utilisateurs, aux réponses aux "
"questions et aux discussions sur le montage vidéo et OpenShot."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you would like to help improve this User Guide, `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."
msgstr ""
"Si vous souhaitez contribuer à l'amélioration de ce guide utilisateur, "
"`consultez la source sur GitHub <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/"
"tree/develop/doc>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you have discovered a new bug, please `Report a Bug <https://www.openshot."
"org/issues/new/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Si vous avez découvert un nouveau bug, veuillez `signaler un bug <https://"
"www.openshot.org/issues/new/>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you need professional support, you can open a ticket by sending an "
"message to support@openshot.org or `Schedule a call <https://calendly.com/"
"openshot-support/desktop>`_."
msgstr ""
"Si vous avez besoin d'un support professionnel, vous pouvez ouvrir un ticket "
"en envoyant un message à support@openshot.org ou `planifier un appel "
"<https://calendly.com/openshot-support/desktop>`_."
